                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Williams</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Uhl</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-12-03">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 3, 1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Superior court of Habana sentenced Sanguily yesterday to imprisonment for
                    life.</p>
            </div>
